Keyboard Fonts ++ app is software, it is complex and may contain bugs (we are really sorry if you have experienced one). While we are doing our best we cannot guarantee that our software will function in all situations and circumstances.
Privacy Policy
This policy applies to all information collected or submitted on Keyboard Fonts ++’s iPhone and iPad app and any other devices and platforms.
Where is my Keyboard Fonts ++ data stored?
Data in the Keyboard Fonts ++ app is private and it is stored only on your mobile device. We do not store or process your data on our servers.
What information is collected about my use of Keyboard Fonts ++?
Certain non-person identifiable information about your use of Keyboard Fonts ++ app (e.g. frequency and duration of usage, significant events and encountered errors if application has crashed etc.) are shared (together with general information about your device - model, operating system version etc.) with Third parties that provide analytics and crash logging services to help us understand how Keyboard Fonts ++ app is used, identify problems early on and improve Keyboard Fonts ++ app experience in future.
At the moment we are relying on
Firebase
for collecting data about app errors/crashes and
Google Analytics
for providing Keyboard Fonts ++ app and website analytics.
What are cookies and how are they used?
When your are browsing Keyboard Fonts ++'s website, small files (known as "cookies") are saved onto your device to collect analytics information about how users browse the site by our analytics service.
Internet address of your computer, tablet or phone is
anonymized
in the analytics service we use and these
cookies are not used to identify you personally
. You can
opt-out
of analytics cookies.
Changes and Updates
If Keyboard Fonts ++ makes changes to Terms and Conditions or Privacy Policy, these changes will be posted on the site in a timely manner. We reserve the right to modify this privacy policy at any time, so please review it frequently (at least on every app update).
In case of a business transaction in which a portion or all of Keyboard Fonts ++ business is acquired, we will notify you as described above in this paragraph.
Contact Us
If you have any questions about these Terms, please contact us.
